Class Description
ChartTabsController
This is an abstract class representing the controllers of all the tabs that displays charts.
Context
A class to enforce singleton on Database class and DateConverter class, so that all the controllers access the same database, instead of instances of datbase.
Controller
Building on the sample skeleton for 'ui.fxml' Controller Class generated by SceneBuilder
Database
A class representing the internal database of the system.
DataTitle
Enum for distinguishing between the title of data.
DateConverter
A Converter that allow conversion between LocalDate objects, long value and String objects mainly for the conversion between the return value of UI elements (such as slider) to an object for internal use.
DayData<T>
An interface representing one day of data within the database
LocationData

MyApplication
